	<h3>In which time zone are the trades shown?</h3><br>
	
	<p>All trade contracts are shown according to your local time zone based on your computer's own internal clock settings.</p><br>
	
	<h3>How is a trade's profit calculated?</h3><br>
	
	<p>The profit for any given trade is displayed at the time the trade contract is made by you. For example if you stake $100 on a trade and your fixed profit is 90% then you will receive $190 if that trade wins, in other words the trade finishes "in-the-money". </p><br>
	
