	<h3>Can I make more than one trade at a time?</h3><br>
	
	<p>Yes. There is no limit to the number of trades you may place! You can place trades on numerous assets </p><br>
	
	<h3>Can I place trades on credit?</h3><br>
	
<p>No. You must have enough money in your account to fund your trade when you place it.</p><br>


<h3>Can I cancel or change trades I placed?</h3><br>

<p>No. You cannot cancel or modify a trade once it has been received and accepted by BTX. This policy is strictly enforced. As you are responsible for all of your trades, make sure that you review and confirm all of the details before placing trades.</p><br>

<h3>How can I verify my trade was made?</h3><br>

<p>All trade positions you place will immediately be confirmed within your "Current Trades" area of the trading page as well as in your "Trade History" in the "Your Account" page. If the trade position is listed then the trade was successfully placed. If the trade is not listed, then it was not placed.</p><br>


	
	
	
